{"tid":1847384,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"醫護之後  入境海關 應該搞工會罷工啦","createTime":"2020-01-28T04:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T06:28:04.000Z","uid":61242,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8b55e91f49ecb751f05a728ff22939416a01a765","tid":1847384,"uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:49:32.000Z","msg":"全世界唔係封關就撤僑<br />\n屌你老母叫你封關就乜乜柒柒<br />\n又要顧蝗感受<br />\n<br />\n醫護清楚病毒恐佈<br />\n特區搵完啲專家出嚟講完<br />\n個撚個戴晒頭盔<br />\n已經唔需要再去證明隻肺炎有幾大鑊<br />\n而家過萬醫護入工會<br />\n但咁係唔撚夠囉<br />\n<br />\n入境海關呢啲高危職業<br />\n你哋自己諗啦<br />\n而家人傳人<br />\n你戴個口罩<br />\n阻得幾多萬人身上嘅病毒<br />\n<br />\n你哋自己唔自救<br />\n有撚人理你哋咩<br />\n仲諗緊自己供緊層樓同鐵飯碗？<br />\n<br />\n你哋有命享先講啦！<br />\n<br />\n跟住醫護搞工會啦<br />\n唔好話你一定罷工<br />\n至少俾個濕鳩政府知道<br />\n你哋唔打算做Condom<br />\n<br />\n藍絲燒村都夠膽<br />\n黃絲一早轄出去<br />\n偽中立最撚怕死<br />\n<br />\n你哋肯跟隊，冇人嘈你哋架！"},{"pid":"52489307d927e0b0407ce52a2bd0e568f9b4aaba","tid":1847384,"uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:51:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28b8ac124a48ef8f94ee934a35748d87b26d273a","tid":1847384,"uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:52:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f63b86a94266106c13a0e651733a24db6396908","tid":1847384,"uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:52:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69029d7dd607596673fe621a555d04572bbcf796","tid":1847384,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:57:25.000Z","msg":"醫護、入境、海關、衞生署成為condom<br />\n高官及文職同你地割蔗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得你地面對大劣人<br />\n文職冷氣軍師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pd0xhvm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPd0xhvm.jpg&h=e650018e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aeabe1c430595b92d94dd90a62c407af70fb88c6","tid":1847384,"uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:59:11.000Z","msg":"幫手推吓好嗎"},{"pid":"f6dd5640250245ff9a5cb02a5b0783d5d1e09b02","tid":1847384,"uid":206344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T06:26:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c24be63a4e55ff06b3819a44b0cf529e905e39c","tid":1847384,"uid":206344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T06:28:04.000Z","msg":"海關嘅工會有冇link？唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}